'''珀納斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Penarth'''}}），是[[英國|英國]]威尔士[[格拉摩根谷|格拉摩根谷]]的一个市镇，位于[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]首府[[加的夫|加的夫]]西南{{convert|8.4|km|mi}}，亦是格拉摩根谷第二大的市鎮<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zoopla.co.uk/property/richlist/uk/wales/ |title=Wales' Highest Value Towns |author=Zoopla |year=2012 |accessdate=2014-07-15 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025082624/http://www.zoopla.co.uk/property/richlist/uk/wales/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，據2011年人口普查統計，常住人口20,396。自[[維多利亞時代|維多利亞時代]]起已經是個度假勝地，有海邊花園（{{lang|en|The Garden by the Sea}}）的美譽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/southeast/sites/penarth/pages/article_davidowen.shtml |title=The Garden by the Sea |author=Owen, David |publisher=BBC Wales |date=22 September 2002 |accessdate=3 March 2012 |archive-date=2010-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101007071719/http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/southeast/sites/penarth/pages/article_davidowen.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。近年[[旅遊業|旅遊業]]於該地已經大不如前，市鎮逐漸轉型為加的夫的[[衛星城市|衛星城市]]，居民每日往返加的夫工作。由於景色怡人，珀納斯亦吸引了不少退休人士來此定居，漸總人口的25%<ref>{{cite book |editor1-first=John |editor1-last=Davies|editor1-link=John Davies (historian)|editor2-first=Nigel |editor2-last=Jenkins | editor2-link=Nigel Jenkins| editor3-first=Baines |editor3-last=Menna|editor4-first=Peredur I. |editor4-last=Lynch|title=The Welsh Academy Encyclopaedia of Wales |year=2008 |page=660 |publisher=University of Wales Press |location=Cardiff |isbn=978-0-7083-1953-6}}</ref>。

